'''Ali Alipour''' ({{langx|fa|علی علیپور}}; born 11 November 1995)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iranleague.ir/league/player/1821|script-title=fa:علي عليپور وب سایت رسمی سازمان لیگ فوتبال ایران,لیگ برتر فوتبال ایران,فوتبال برتر|website=iranleague.ir|language=fa|access-date=24 June 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831214357/http://www.iranleague.ir/league/player/1821|archive-date=31 August 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref> is an [[Iranian peoples|Iranian]] professional [[Football player|footballer]] who plays as a [[Striker (association football)|Striker]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] club [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].

At the age of 19 years and 185 days, Alipour was the youngest-ever player to score in the [[Tehran derby]] after scoring in [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]] 1–0 victory on 15 May 2015. He is the only player in Tehran derby history who has scored the winning goal in two derby matches.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://90tv.ir/news/423013/%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%B1%DA%A9%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AE-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%B4%D8%AF|title=90tv.ir {{!}} وبسایت رسمی برنامه ۹۰ – علی علیپور رکورددار تاریخ دربی شد|work=90tv.ir {{!}} وبسایت رسمی برنامه ۹۰ -|access-date=2018-04-16|language=fa|archive-date=3 November 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103012957/http://90tv.ir/news/423013/%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%B1%DA%A9%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AE-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%B4%D8%AF|url-status=dead}}</ref>

==Club career==
Alipour started his career with [[Nassaji Mazandaran F.C.|Nassaji Mazandaran]]. He made his professional debut in 2012 at the age of 16 with [[Azadegan League]] club [[Sang Ahan Bafq F.C.|Sang Ahan Bafq]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1374569|title=علیپور: با ساچمه هم نمی‌شود به بیرانوند گل زد :: ورزش سه|website=varzesh3.com|language=fa|access-date=2016-11-23}}</ref>

===Persepolis===
[[File:Ali Alipour in Persepolis FC and FC Nasaf Match.jpg|thumb|Alipour, pictured playing against [[FC Nasaf|Nasaf]] in the [[2018 AFC Champions League]]]]
Alipour signed with [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]] in January 2015.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://irannewsdaily.com/persepolis-striker-alipour-invited-national-team-report/|title=Persepolis Striker Alipour Invited to National Team: Report – irannews|date=2018-02-13|work=irannews|access-date=2018-04-16|language=en-US|archive-date=18 June 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618052515/http://irannewsdaily.com/persepolis-striker-alipour-invited-national-team-report/|url-status=live}}</ref> He scored his first goal for the club on 11 March 2015 in a 2–2 draw against [[Naft Masjed Soleyman F.C.|Naft Masjed Soleyman]]. On 15 May, Alipour scored in the [[Tehran derby]] against [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]], making him the youngest player to score in the Tehran derby at 19 years old.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2018/02/13/1656107/persepolis-striker-alipour-invited-to-national-team-report|title=Persepolis Striker Alipour Invited to National Team: Report – Tasnim News Agency|work=Tasnim News Agency|access-date=2018-04-16|language=en|archive-date=11 May 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511112352/https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2018/02/13/1656107/persepolis-striker-alipour-invited-to-national-team-report|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.varzesh3.com/news/1240546/%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%AC%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C%D9%86-%DA%AF%D9%84%D8%B2%D9%86-%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AE-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C|title=علی علیپور جوان ترین گلزن تاریخ دربی :: ورزش سه|website=varzesh3.com|language=fa|access-date=2018-04-16}}</ref> On 26 March 2016, Alipour scored his first hat-trick for the club in a 6–4 friendly win against Omani champions [[Al-Oruba SC|Al-Oruba]].

He was the [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] top goalscorer in [[2017–18 Persian Gulf Pro League|2017–18]], tallying 19 goals.<ref>[https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1645556/%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C%D9%86-%DA%AF%D9%84%D8%B2%D9%86-%D9%84%DB%8C%DA%AF-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3-%D8%B4%D8%AF Alipour became Persepolis' top scorer in the Premier League]</ref>

===C.S. Marítimo===
On 28 September 2020, Alipour joined [[Portuguese people|Portuguese]] [[Primeira Liga]] club [[C.S. Marítimo|Marítimo]] on a two-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=BEM-VINDO ALI ALIPOUR |url=https://www.csmaritimo.org.pt/bem-vindo-ali-alipour/ |website=C.S. Marítimo |date=28 September 2020 |access-date=29 September 2020 |archive-date=28 September 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928222555/https://www.csmaritimo.org.pt/bem-vindo-ali-alipour/ |url-status=live }}</ref>

He helped the team in many important matches and was one of the key players of the team in the front line.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-04-24 |title=ببینید{{!}} بازگشت بزرگ ماریتیمو با درخشش علی علی پور {{!}} گل دیدنی مهاجم ایرانی برای فرار از شکست |url=https://www.hamshahrionline.ir/news/671856/%D8%A8%D8%A8%DB%8C%D9%86%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DA%AF%D8%B4%D8%AA-%D8%A8%D8%B2%D8%B1%DA%AF-%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85%D9%88-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%AE%D8%B4%D8%B4-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%86%DB%8C |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=همشهری آنلاین |language=fa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-02-15 |title=خبرگزاری فارس - لیگ فوتبال پرتغال{{!}} پیروزی ماریتیمو با درخشش مهاجم ایرانی/2 گل علیپور در قعر دروازه آروکا+فیلم |url=https://www.farsnews.ir/news/14001126000047/%D9%84%DB%8C%DA%AF-%D9%81%D9%88%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%BA%D8%A7%D9%84{{pipe}}-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85%D9%88-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%AE%D8%B4%D8%B4-%D9%85%D9%87%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%85-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86%DB%8C-2-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1 |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=خبرگزاری فارس}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2021-04-25 |title=ببینید {{!}} پیروزی ماریتیمو با درخشش عابدزاده و گل تماشایی علیپور |url=https://www.khabaronline.ir/news/1508636/%D8%A8%D8%A8%DB%8C%D9%86%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85%D9%88-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%AE%D8%B4%D8%B4-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%AF%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%87-%D9%88-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%AA%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%A7%DB%8C%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1 |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=www.khabaronline.ir |language=fa}}</ref>

=== Gil Vicente ===
On 18 May 2022, Alipour joined Portuguese club [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-07-19 |title=علی علیپور به ژیل ویسنته پرتغال پیوست |url=https://donya-e-eqtesad.com/%D8%A8%D8%AE%D8%B4-%D8%B3%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%AE%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%86-62/3866483-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D9%87-%DA%98%DB%8C%D9%84-%D9%88%DB%8C%D8%B3%D9%86%D8%AA%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%BA%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=روزنامه دنیای اقتصاد |language=fa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-05-18 |title=علی علیپور به ژیل ویسنته پیوست |url=https://www.isna.ir/news/1401022819501/%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D9%87-%DA%98%DB%8C%D9%84-%D9%88%DB%8C%D8%B3%D9%86%D8%AA%D9%87-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=ایسنا |language=fa}}</ref> At this time, he was also linked to his previous club, Persepolis.<ref>{{Cite web |last=فوتبال |first=خبرگزاری پارس |date=2022-05-19 |title=علی علیپور به ژیل ویسنته‌ پیوست ؛ پرسپولیس گزینه اصلی برای خط حمله را از دست داد |url=https://parsfootball.com/na/?p=100804 |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=پارس فوتبال {{!}} خبرگزاری فوتبال ایران {{!}} ParsFootball |language=fa-IR}}</ref><ref>[https://www.irna.ir/news/85542317/%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DA%AF%D8%B4%D8%AA-%D8%A2%D9%82%D8%A7%DB%8C-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%A8%D8%B9%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%DB%B4-%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA بازگشت آقای گل بعد از ۴ سال؛ علیپور به پرسپولیس پیوست]</ref><ref>[https://video.varzesh3.com/video/347786/%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DA%AF%D8%B4%D8%AA-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3 بازگشت علی علیپور به پرسپولیس]</ref><ref>[https://football360.ir/post/2024071727/%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DA%AF%D8%B4%D8%AA-%D8%A2%D9%82%D8%A7%DB%8C-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%AC%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%AE%D9%87%D8%A7-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3%DB%8C-%D8%B4%D8%AF بازگشت آقای گل به جمع سرخ‌ها؛ علی علیپور دوباره پرسپولیسی شد]</ref>

===Return to Persepolis===
On 19 July 2024, Alipour joined [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] side Persepolis with another contract.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-07-19 |title=Persepolis complete signing of Ali Alipour |url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/501248/Persepolis-complete-signing-of-Ali-Alipour |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=Tehran Times |language=en}}</ref> He was also linked to [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal Tehran]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Gil Vicente Forward Alipour Reaches Agreement with Persepolis - Sports news |url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2024/07/18/3124087/gil-vicente-forward-alipour-reaches-agreement-with-persepolis |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=Tasnim News Agency |language=en}}</ref> After signing the contract with Persepolis he said: "I came back with full concentration and calm thinking, and I'm very happy that it happened".<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-07-18 |title=(Alipour after returning to Persepolis: I apologize to Esteghlalis) علیپور پس از بازگشت به پرسپولیس: از استقلالی‌ها معذرت می‌خوام! |url=https://www.khabaronline.ir/news/1933910/%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%86-%D8%B5%D8%AD%D8%A8%D8%AA-%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D9%BE%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DA%AF%D8%B4%D8%AA-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3 |access-date=2024-07-19 |website=www.khabaronline.ir |language=fa}}</ref>

==International career==
[[File:Iran mens national football team training 125 (cropped).jpg|thumb|199x199px|Alipour in [[Iran national football team|Iran]] training in 2019.]]
Alipour was called up to the [[Iran national football team]] in March 2017.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.khabarvarzeshi.com/fa/news/111401|title=6 پرسپولیسی به تیم ملی دعوت شدند|last=خبرورزشی|date=2020-01-01|website=fa|language=fa|access-date=2020-01-01}}</ref> He made his debut against [[Sierra Leone national football team|Sierra Leone]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jamaran.ir/بخش-%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%B2%D8%B4%DB%8C-160/886103-%D8%AD%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B4%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B2-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3-%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AF%DA%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A6%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%AF%DB%8C%D9%88%D9%85|title=حواشی بازی امروز تیم ملی/ عکس یادگاری بازیکنان سیرالئون با استادیوم!|website=پایگاه خبری جماران – امام خمینی – انقلاب اسلامی|date=17 March 2018 |language=fa|access-date=2020-01-01}}</ref> on 17 March 2018 in a friendly match.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.isna.ir/news/96122614537/%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B4%DB%8C%D9%87-%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D9%86%DB%8C%D9%85%D9%87-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%88-%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A6%D9%88%D9%86|title=حاشیه‌های نیمه دوم بازی‌ ایران و سیرالئون|date=2018-03-17|website=ایسنا|language=fa|access-date=2020-01-01|archive-date=1 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101172122/https://www.isna.ir/news/96122614537/%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B4%DB%8C%D9%87-%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D9%86%DB%8C%D9%85%D9%87-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%88-%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A6%D9%88%D9%86|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mashreghnews.ir/photo/840628/%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%BE%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%DA%86%D9%87-%D8%B4%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%87-%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C-%DA%